text: Ada Smolnikar (born 1935) is a Slovenian gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Jesenice, Jesenice
